FR 5: Restricted Data Flow

Requirement ST-T1024 Implementation
Network segmentation Air-gapped — no network.
Zones and conduits Tiles are natural zones. No conduits between them.
Firewall Not needed — no network traffic.

ST-T1024 Position: Exceptional — no network = no attack vector.

