FR 6: Timely Response to Events

Requirement ST-T1024 Implementation
Event detection FSM cycle counter detects execution anomalies.
Response AET enforcement halts execution if timing violated.
Audit logging FSM states are logged in hardware.
Reporting 0x-AMBIG output for any ambiguity.

ST-T1024 Position: Excellent — hardware-enforced AET provides guaranteed response.

