FR 7: Resource Availability

Requirement ST-T1024 Implementation
DoS protection AET = 680 ns — no infinite loops. Power gating = no energy exhaustion.
Resource management Only one tile active at a time. Minimal resource usage.
Redundancy Multiple tiles provide logical redundancy.

ST-T1024 Position: Outstanding — AET physically prevents denial-of-service.

