SL 2 Protection against intentional violation using simple means ✅ Achieved — FIS triage + tile isolation
SL 3 Protection against intentional violation using sophisticated means ✅ Achievable — SL 3 with formal verification + FMEDA
SL 4 Protection against intentional violation using advanced means ⚠️ Requires additional measures — triple-redundant tiles, intrusion detection

